Description: Fix CVE-2022-25896 - Session fixation on login and logout
 When a user logs in or logs out, regenerate the session ID to prevent
 session fixation attacks. Backport of upstream passport 0.6.0 fix from
 PR #900 (commit 42630cbd1ffd44d146ff96f0a4be6f3c12f81d75).
Origin: upstream, https://github.com/jaredhanson/passport/pull/900
Author: Jared Hanson <jaredhanson@gmail.com>
Applied-By: Automated Security Patching System
Bug: CVE-2022-25896
CVSS: 4.8 (Medium)
CWE: CWE-384 (Session Fixation)

